data.description: Welcome to your dream retreat nestled on a picturesque 5 acre- parcel. This stunning property offers a blend of modern design, privacy, and breathtaking natural surroundings. Experience the beauty of natural light streaming through the strategically placed skylights, illuminating the spacious and open floor plan. The thoughtfully designed layout creates a seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quality family time. This loan is assumable with 4% interest for those who qualify. Sellers are very motivated.
